				<h3>User Testing</h3>
		<!--</div>	-->					   				   
					<p>My user research/usability/user testing service provides evidence for decisions with regards to the design, allowing you to understand how users interact with the design. In addition, expert heuristic evaluations are carried out, where the design is evaluated against a set of researched criteria according to your users. Also, personas are created to provide a representation of your 'typical' user in order to find and understand their interactions.</p>
